Description:
Amazing Views and Striking Watergate Style
Displaying sensational westerly views which take in the neighbouring Docklands Park as well as out to the tranquil waters of Port Phillip Bay, this excellent 105 sq.m approx. two bedroom, two bathroom Watergate apartment will captivate all with its contemporary elegance and standout Victoria Harbour location.
Inside this 15th floor retreat you can enjoy memorable views from the expansive central living zone which promises specific lounge and dining spaces, as well as the full-length undercover balcony. The immaculate kitchen just off the entry is another major highlight delivering a stainless steel breakfast bar and appliances.
Both bedrooms come with their own unique advantages. The master bedroom enjoys a walk-in robe and private ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom has a built-in robe and study nook. Also embrace a stylish bathroom with laundry, central heating and cooling, video intercom entry, secure car space, and access to facilities including a pool, sauna, and gym.
The amazing harbour precinct offers the convenience of the CBD just a short walk away, as well as access to terrific eateries including The Hof Downtown, The Spice Dine, and Twirled Pasta Bar just to name a few. You’re also right near The Hub @ Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Woolworths Victoria Harbour, and trams on Harbour Esplanade.
Please call Clare Thompson on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive viewing.
Insights: 1501/18 Waterview Walk, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2019 and 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Great Value Two Bedroom Apartment at the Convesso
Here is a golden opportunity to own an affordable apartment located on an absolute prime water frontage 5 star building in the heart of Victoria Harbour, Docklands.
On offer is a spectacular two bedroom, one bathroom apartment with a secure car space on the 14th floor of the magnificent Convesso building. Located right at the waterfront of Victoria Harbour, the Convesso Building is designed to maximise views over the Harbour, the Bay and the City Skyline. It is conveniently situated close to restaurants, shopping, Etihad Stadium, Southern Cross Station and within a few minutes' drive to Melbourne's CBD.
With a level of amenity similar to that of exclusive 5 star boutique hotels, the Convesso offers:
- 24 hour concierge
- North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities
- 25 metre pool, spa and sauna
- Gymnasium and treatment room
- Cinema
- Residents Lounge
- Board Room
Experience modern living at its finest with state of the art facilities that cater to every lifestyle. Don't wait any longer! Please call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999

Description:
Perfect 1st home owner’s abode!
Situated in the North Tower of the prestigious Watergate development, this beautiful two bedroom one bathroom apartment with one carpark is bathed in natural light and located high up on the 16th floor, enjoying wonderful easterly views of the CBD.
Features of this cosy home include:
- A wonderfully defined living area,
- Fully functional kitchen with stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar,
- Two spacious bedrooms with built-in wardrobes,
- The main bedroom with ensuite access and study nook,
- Reverse cycle air-conditioning, cross ventilation system,
- Private balcony with panoramic city views,
- One secure undercover car park.
In terms of location, it could not be better with restaurants, bars, Etihad Stadium, parklands and public transport at your doorstep. This glorious apartment is also in close vicinity to the CBD, South Wharf, Harbour Town and Crown entertainment complex and the accessibility of the freeways is only a minute away. The incredible Docklands precinct presents not only modern living, but a lifestyle one can only dream of.
This spacious apartment is ideal for the first home owner or the astute investor.
Do not delay to inspect this apartment as this gem is sure to be snapped up!

Description:
An Inspirational New Offering with Amazing CBD Views
Grab a slice of the utterly luxurious, relaxed, and comfortable Docklands life with this brand new dual level one bedroom apartment with a northern orientation, which has an enviable location in Yarra’s Edge newest residential jewel, ‘Forge Apartments’.
An incredibly unique floorplan is split into two distinct levels allowing for dedicated and private areas to live and sleep. The generous living zone has an abundance of space for both lounge and dining while also integrating the stylish stone kitchen which is pleasing on the eye with elegant cabinetry and stainless steel appliances.
The balcony via a sliding floor-to-ceiling glass door feeds off the living zone and displays exceptional views of the city in the distance as well as the Yarra River, meanwhile on its own secluded level is the sizeable bedroom offering a built-in robe and the immaculate bathroom. Other extras are a European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom entry, and secure car space.
The benefit of living in the Forge complex is that you get to enjoy being part of the new Wharf’s Entrance area of the precinct, which offers a quiet and village-like lifestyle as well as a facilities including Wharf’s Club with gym and pool, and a private kitchen/dining room and cinema for you to use at your own leisure.
You’re also located seconds to South Wharf bars and restaurants including The General Assembly, Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, Charlie Lovett, and Munich Brauhaus, while you can also walk to Crown Casino, CBD, and public transport including Southern Cross Station.

Description:
City Fringe Living with Waterfront Views
Making the most of its elevated setting in the coveted Boyd residential complex in New Quay, this apartment revels in grandstand views of the shimmering water of the Marina and the bright city lights of the CBD.
A wonderful blend of contemporary style and practicality, the apartment boasts a large master bedroom with walk-in robe and ensuite with marble vanity as well as generous second and third bedrooms, both with built-in robes.
The open plan living space encompasses a well appointed and functional entertainers kitchen with glossy granite benchtops and Miele stove and dishwasher. Ample space for living and dining creates an irresistible invitation out to the balcony which lends its self effortlessly to a glass of wine of a night, looking out over the outstanding city skyline.
Other features include separate laundry, second bathroom, powder room, NBN connection, ducted air conditioning, two secure car spaces and storage cage.
The building itself offers all residents access to first class amenities including alfresco barbecue area, swimming pool and gymnasium - pure indulgence! Local restaurants, cafes, HarbourTown shopping centre, Southern Cross Station and tram stops with in the free tram zone are all at your doorstep.

Description:
Unparalleled Views, Exceptional Style & Nonstop Luxury.
First home buyers in search of living the charmed Docklands lifestyle need not look any further than this modern and relaxed one bedroom apartment in the esteemed 'The Quays' complex.
Also suited for smart investors, this picture perfect modern city pad is perched high up on the 21st floor.This retreat has a sensational living and meals zone, which opens out to a west-facing balcony which is ideal for drinks and dinners in the warm summer months.
The designer kitchen includes an abundance of storage space, gas cooking and an integrated fridge and freezer. Your master bedroom is spacious with plenty of wardrobe space and is serviced by the sparkling central bathroom with a neatly tucked away European laundry.
The Quays building offers state of the art access to the swimming pool, spa, gymnasium, function room, studio, cinema room and tennis court to all residents and is situated in prime position to free trams, Harbour Town shopping, cafes and restaurants, the glistening Marina and Etihad Stadium, walking distance to Southern Cross Station and Crown Casino with Victoria Market, CBD and beaches well within reach

Description:
Magnificent Mosaic
Piece by piece, the Docklands precinct is forming into a picture perfect place to live. Surrounded by parklands and the water aspect of the harbour, there is no wonder why so many residents are happily calling Docklands home.
The "Mosaic" is one of Docklands rare low rise boutique residential apartment complexes. Only 9 levels in height, the residential complex is located in the heart of trendy Bourke Street Docklands.
On offer is this well equipped 2 bedroom apartment and wide balcony which is perfect for entertaining or just relaxing. The apartment has a gourmet styled kitchen with stainless steel appliances and stone bench tops. An open plan living and dining area has floor to ceiling windows and overlooks the green open spaces below. The main bedroom has built in robes and adjoins the fully tiled central bathroom. Other features include split system air conditioning / heating, European style laundry, one secure car space on title.
Amazing 3 storage cages! A rare plus feature indeed.
Beautiful views of the park and walking distance to the CBD, with public transport at your front door.

Description:
BLUE CHIP INVESTMENT
Attention investors, don't miss out on this beautiful and contemporary 2 bedroom opportunity at M Docklands, featuring remarkable styling, amazing views and returns of 5.8% with 11 months to run on the lease.
The open plan kitchen/dining area includes an island bench with breakfast bar, concealed dishwasher, Bosch oven and cooktop, concealed fridge, and plenty of clever storage solutions. The light-filled living room flows out onto the balcony with breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour to the west, and Mount Macedon to the north. Both bedrooms come with mirrored BIRs. The strikingly designed bathroom features timber finishes, black fixtures, and subway tiling in the shower, which includes a rain-shower head.
Rounding out this remarkable apartment is a Euro-laundry, secure swipe and video intercom entry, secure car space, and storage cage. Typical of modern apartment living residents enjoy the use of the complex's gym and heated outdoor swimming pool. In addition to these amenities, residents can take advantage of Peppers Privileges such as home delivery from the Momami Restaurant and vehicle detailing.
With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this inner city pad is perfectly situated on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD, and is only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
Stunning Loft Living Is a Class Above The Rest
Positioned in the Silver Tower of the fantastic Aqui Promenade development and enjoying a high level of lavish sophistication, this brilliant dual level two bedroom loft apartment is something special right on the cusp of the picturesque Victoria Harbour.
Filled with stunning natural light and conveying an almost New York style feel with its open space, this apartment is a must for owner-occupiers who have a keen eye for detail and want to live a luxurious Docklands lifestyle. Natural timber oak floors line the ground level, which features generous living and dining wonderfully serviced by a gourmet stone kitchen with stainless steel European appliances.
The ground level also offers up a sizeable bedroom with built-in robes, vibrant bathroom with floor-to-ceiling tiles and a large shower, and a private balcony. The 2nd bedroom has its own private space upstairs and also comes with BIRs, meanwhile other property features include a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and car space. Residents of this fabulous complex also have access to an indoor 25m swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and lobby with private meeting rooms.
This standout property is located in the heart of the NewQuay precinct. You have wonderful cafes right at your doorstep, while you’re just an easy stroll to Waterfront City, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, and Etihad Stadium. You’re also close to Southern Cross Station as well as trams which take you to the CBD, Richmond, Hawthorn, Box Hill, and Preston.
Please call Mariecris Tagala on 0410 430 508 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

This incredible luxury townhouse ticks all the boxes, space, convenience, style and location which blend together to provide the ultimate inner-city lifestyle.
